race.comment: BACARDI GIRL (1) was in the money last time at this track (30.79) in a Grade 6, finishing a 2.5 lengths third. Has already won out of this draw. Looks the one to beat with even luck. COOL BLUE YOU (2) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 5th (31.17) at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Worth following up. ADHANA MARTINA (8) has been in super consistent form recently with three minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fourth (31.37) at this track. Worth another chance. ADHANA KEVIN (4) collected a minor prize last start over this track and distance - must be considered.
